  "detailed_description": "Save the scientists and unlock powerful weapons!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1389750/extras/5ea6c116317b602ba957e46cb606c5ae.poster.avif?t=1709033083\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1389750/extras/5ea6c116317b602ba957e46cb606c5ae.webm?t=1709033083\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1389750/extras/5ea6c116317b602ba957e46cb606c5ae.mp4?t=1709033083\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Hybrid realtime-turn based system! Enemies react to your actions - if you are in trouble, stop and think!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1389750/extras/0c73e5716a534f3f36e17f66c9162577.poster.avif?t=1709033083\" width=616 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1389750/extras/0c73e5716a534f3f36e17f66c9162577.webm?t=1709033083\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1389750/extras/0c73e5716a534f3f36e17f66c9162577.mp4?t=1709033083\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>6 playable characters, each with a unique playing style!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1389750/extras/a06b186ede934c275086a5dfc27381ba.poster.avif?t=1709033083\" width=616 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1389750/extras/a06b186ede934c275086a5dfc27381ba.webm?t=1709033083\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1389750/extras/a06b186ede934c275086a5dfc27381ba.mp4?t=1709033083\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>A story about love, hate and robots<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1389750/extras/3515c25a4c80f8c656d915bd041f3a88.poster.avif?t=1709033083\" width=616 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1389750/extras/3515c25a4c80f8c656d915bd041f3a88.webm?t=1709033083\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1389750/extras/3515c25a4c80f8c656d915bd041f3a88.mp4?t=1709033083\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1389750/extras/29649b03fa38377c08b66eb4af45733e.avif?t=1709033083\" width=616 height=166 /></span><br>During the early 70s, the government created a secret robot city, controlled by a supercomputer called PAL 9000. One day, PAL 9000 went out of control, and rebelled against his creators.<br>As Julie, a rookie agent, your goal is to find all your captured teammates and defeat the evil PAL 9000.<br><strong>But... are you sure you're on the right side? Are you sure robots are the aggressors?</strong>",
